Bieber wears a turtleneck by Emporio Armani. See complete credits.“What do I love about Justin? Everything!” said Justin’s lucky lunch date. Her favorite part of the meal? Ice-cold lemonade, with an afternoon serenade on the side.
Bieber wears a cardigan by Band of Outsiders; T-shirt by the Gap; pants by Unis; shoes by Keds. See complete credits.Dreads over threads, Justin’s clothes were waterlogged while, at his insistence, his hair remained dry. Moments later, Justin and his team jetted to board a private plane to San Diego, so he’d have enough time to meet more fans before his arena show that night.
