Complex Presents: Justin Bieber And Michael Rapaport In "Bieber vs. Rapaport: More Than A Game"

		  Global superstar Justin Bieber and veteran actor Michael Rapaport take to the court in an epic rematch for MVP status in the wake of Bieber's October/November cover story.
		

Sep 30, 2015, 15:00 ET
		  		  														
						 from   Complex 











 
















































 

 




















 


NEW YORK, Sept. 30, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- It's the sports rivalry you never knew existed––the celebrity feud you've been waiting for. Complex's October/November cover star Justin Bieber and veteran (washed up?) actor Michael Rapaport first met at the All-Star Celebrity Games. But when Bieber robbed Rapaport of the MVP crown in 2011, the aging actor's life went into a downward spiral while Justin's star just kept rising.
In the aftermath of this epic rivalry, Complex follows Rapaport as he preps for a re-match with Bieber––who clearly hasn't given it much thought. 
Justin Bieber is currently on the cover of Complex's October/November issue, which has been said to be his most revealing interview yet. He speaks on the his relationship with Selena Gomez, his arrest in Miami, and his relationship with God. 
Watch as Bieber and Rapaport battle it out on Complex's court. Will Rapaport take back his MVP title? Can Justin be stopped? You've got to watch to find out. 
YouTube link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T6tUpMK2dnA
Starring: Justin Bieber as himself, Michael Rapaport, as himself, Scooter Braun as himself
Directors: Michael Rapaport and Marc Fernandez
Contact: Carmen Villafane, carmenv@complex.com
Who is COMPLEX?
Complex is a media platform and an online community that publishes the best, most diverse and most relevant voices in culture, period. With over 140 million unique monthly visitors and 1.4B monthly pageviews, Complex makes culture pop from its collection of partners, brands and its hub site Complex.com for one of the most sought after audiences of millennial influencers ever assembled.
 
